name: Nofreetime
overview:
Nofreetime.com is a free to use wedding website and wedding venue directory providing free comprehensive wedding planning advice, resources, tips and ideas for every budget to help with every aspect of wedding planning

Nofreetime.com can help with every aspect of wedding planning from making the initial key decisions and setting the budget to changing your name after your wedding day.

Couples can download a free wedding checklist and free wedding invitation and other wedding stationery templates from the website. Nofreetime also includes lots of different forms of wedding invitation wording.

Nofreetime.com also provides useful tips, ideas and questions to ask to help couples find the perfect wedding venue, photographer, musician, toastmaster, flowers, invitations or wedding cake.

The website also includes advice and guides for other members of the wedding party.
